試說明奈米抗體結構及在生物技術應用上的優點與限制。（15分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "61985cf4779f", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "409", "s": "2208", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "生物技術學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "衛生技術"}'::jsonb, NULL),
